You're also helping
to keep people safe.

5
00:00:13.140 --> 00:00:16.320
Breaches that affect
customers', vendors',

6
00:00:16.320 --> 00:00:20.280
and employees' data can
cause significant damage to

7
00:00:20.280 --> 00:00:24.510
people's financial stability
and their reputations.

8
00:00:24.510 --> 00:00:27.675
As an analyst, your
day-to-day work

9
00:00:27.675 --> 00:00:31.320
