we'll discuss security
frameworks, controls,

12
00:00:37.215 --> 00:00:41.180
and design principles in more
detail, and how they can be

13
00:00:41.180 --> 00:00:43.550
applied to security
audits to help

14
00:00:43.550 --> 00:00:46.390
protect organizations
and people.

15
00:00:47.390 --> 00:00:49.340
Keeping customer
information confidential is

16
00:00:49.340 --> 00:00:52.700
a crucial part of my
daily work at Google.

17
00:00:52.700 --> 00:00:55.385
The NIST Cybersecurity Framework

18
00:00:55.385 --> 00:00:57.380
plays a large part in this.

19
